Fucking hell, grrrr.... Frustrated beyond all hell, blog isn't helping. I am what I make of myself. I am Love. I am. Off to a training, not back til Sunday. So tired. So in pain. Starbucks will make it all better, I know it ! Fuck. Okay, file another tragic story in a box of my mind to be dealt with when I no longer have a heart. Love to all of my beautiful friends and family for the support and awesomeness of who they are. I'm gonna die young but happy. Rather than healthy and old. Got the new iPhone 3GS. Don't ask how, I won't tell you. But thank you. Some people say pain can be controlled by the mind. I do not agree with these people. It doesn't mean I don't admire them though. Writing, then 2 chapters homework, then bed. Or just Loveline ? Home...finally. Sooooo tired...gonna get a couple hours before work starts up again. Getting together map, snacks, music, and up-all-night accessories for Hollywood. Will starting driving at 4 am. Not tired, must sleep. Long week ahead, and no weekend. Friday is no longer a day off. Sore all over, but I asked for it. Cig, Loveline, sleep...smile, love, remember. "For a moment I love everything I see and think and feel..." "I like my chicken fried, a cold beer on a friday night, a pair of jeans that fit just right, and the radio up !" Fucking musicians. Fuck musicians... Today was a much needed day off !! Back to a fake smile tomorrow, but rejuvinated by friends tonight. I always want the blog to be the magical valve. Turn it on, write, be healed. It never is though. And now I still hurt, I just feel more raw now. As long as I stay with the emotion and don't deny...I'll be alright.
